title: VA Indie Electro Rock August 2013 - Dust Clears (Dutch Treat I3)
description:
A quite definite preview of the second Dutch Treat Indie Playlist of August. A bit more Chill than Rock this time.

I must assume that the Rockers already are dreaming about their oncoming holidays. Still quite nice though.... Enjoy,
